Neuronvisio
------------

Neuronvisio is a GTK2 user interface for NEURON simulator http://www.neuron.yale.edu/neuron/. 
Neuronvisio use the python interface of NEURON and runs in its own thread.

This gives the possibility to use ipython and modify the model runtime.

Home Page:
http://mattions.github.com/neuronvisio/

Documentation:
On the wiki when ready
http://wiki.github.com/mattions/neuronvisio
